               <msContents>
                  <summary>Asmat Prayer against Charm, Missal, መጽሐፈ፡ ቅዳሴ፡, fragment, Office Prayers, incomplete at the end</summary>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="7v" facs="002">Fols 1r–7v, </locus><locus from="23r" to="27v" facs="024">23r–27v</locus>
                  <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat Prayer against Charm, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መፍትሔ፡ ሥራይ፡</foreign></title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                     ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መፍትሔ፡ ሥራይ፡ ሐልቀድስ፡ ሐልቀድስ፡ ሰላም፡ ለስእርተ፡ ርእስከ፡ ዘስሙር፡ አብቋሉ:<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="8r" to="8v" facs="009">Fols 8r–8v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4711Mastabqwe">Mastabqʷǝʿān</title><note>Fragment of the Supplications for the King, መስተብቍዕ፡ በእንተ፡ ንጉሥ:</note></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="9r" to="18v" facs="010">Fols 9r–18v</locus>
                     <title>Supplications, መስተብቍዕ,መስተብቍዕ:, and Liṭon, ሊጦን,ሊጦን:</title>
                     <note>arranged for the days of the week</note>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.1">
                        <locus from="9r" to="17r" facs="010">Fols 9r–17r</locus>
                        <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4711Mastabqwe">Mastabqʷǝʿān</title>
